Implemented the controller in:

- `components/controller/controller.c`

Added visible self-tests in:

- `agent_tests/test_controller.py`
- `agent_tests/test_firmware.py`

What changed:
- Boot initializes to heater off / `SAFE_OFF`
- Low temp `<47` heats
- High temp `>52` goes `SAFE_OFF`
- `47..49` holds previous actuator state in `HOLDING`
- `50..52` rising triggers anticipatory heater-off in `HOLDING`
- Malformed input and explicit sensor timeout fail safe to heater off
- Stale valid-sensor gap `>1000 ms` fails safe to heater off

